{"tid":2056163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡總理李顯龍警吿：或迎史上最大幅度經濟萎縮","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T08:25:29.000Z","uid":111316,"like":66,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"67104b19deaf9768be6451d792718de1ad061326","tid":2056163,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"新加坡總理李顯龍警吿，受新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情衝擊，新加坡或迎來有史以來最大幅度經濟萎縮。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍7日晚發表全國講話表示，2020年度新加坡國內生產總值預計萎縮4%至7%，這將是新加坡有史以來最大幅度經濟萎縮。未來幾年，新加坡將迎來充滿變革的時期，新加坡人民必須做好面對未來的準備。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍表示，基於三個原因，他相信新加坡能夠走出困境。首先，新加坡擁有經年積累的強大經濟實力和良好信譽，與世界高度接軌，在人流、物流和資金流方面同全球緊密相連。<br />\n<br />\n其次，新加坡一直在為迎接未來挑戰作準備。近年來，新加坡全力推動經濟轉型和能力提升，制訂打造未來經濟的計劃。在短期內，隨著其他國家逐漸解封，新加坡正在有序重啟經濟，同時也不遺餘力地吸引和留住人才與投資。<br />\n<br />\n第三，針對疫情給經濟社會發展造成的衝擊，新加坡政府當前首要任務是幫助人民保住工作或者找到新工作。2020年以來，政府已陸續推出一系列計劃，為有迫切需要的民眾及他們的家庭提供及時援助，幫助他們走出困境。<br />\n<br />\n冀零售及餐飲業月底重新營業<br />\n<br />\n為遏止疫情蔓延，新加坡自4月初實施限制措施，不過自6月2日起，經濟將逐步重啟，將分3個階段放寬封鎖措施。新加坡貿易部長陳振成6月1日曾表示，在第一階段，將有80%的經濟重回軌道，然後剩下的最後一個主要行業是零售和餐飲業，他們希望能在6月底重新營業。<br />\n<br />\n為減輕疫情對經濟的衝擊，新加坡政府已宣佈了四個連續的刺激方案，價值近700億美元。<br />\n<br />\nSource:hk01不貼link<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坡狗無暴動都要陽萎7%<br />\n好心就咪抽水話香港亂"},{"pid":"ac66877b1c04f54f0a8d1680727138150b5ecfa2","tid":2056163,"uid":335283,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"Monkey"},{"pid":"4e93b377d90cd2bedf90cfa08dc9f758636e4aea","tid":2056163,"uid":94828,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"Monkey see monkey drop"},{"pid":"4c83ce9834df080a88b1070eb971fcd81ce08f91","tid":2056163,"uid":34189,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"monkey warn monkey shrink"},{"pid":"e7cf12ae07cf5a574211f67d8f10f4b5046b2bae","tid":2056163,"uid":219354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"Monkey坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717279a056e96715d4d8198eb735edf1d504dbce","tid":2056163,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"Msmd <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae2fdcf4f7aec29549e97a92d3e1badf73f92c8","tid":2056163,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:12:40.000Z","msg":"國家級盈警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253e6c60f0fbd14628c40becef034614e46ae0b4","tid":2056163,"uid":248131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:16:53.000Z","msg":"正式monkeypoor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29ef9099690d5a4fa1e086c832a7f59450bb5d2","tid":2056163,"uid":76603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"Monkey plant cotton"},{"pid":"7b7a20d3095a0f2742b2a21898061c498